WEBVTT

00:00:11.641 --> 00:00:15.224
Every day, a sea of decisions 
stretches before us.

00:00:15.224 --> 00:00:17.059
Some are small and unimportant,

00:00:17.059 --> 00:00:19.599
but others have a larger impact 
on our lives.

00:00:19.599 --> 00:00:22.304
For example, which politician
should I vote for?

00:00:22.304 --> 00:00:24.493
Should I try the latest diet craze?

00:00:24.493 --> 00:00:27.416
Or will email make me a millionaire?

00:00:27.416 --> 00:00:30.127
We're bombarded with so many decisions